title: Special announcement and Andy Cohen ReRealease
description: Danielle and Casey are off doing their special Bitch Sesh Live from home Halloween Hangover show featuring Andy Cohen (which you can still watch on VOD for the next week at loopedlive.com) but please listen to this gorgeous episode from the archives featuring our lord and savior himself and we'll see you next week.
